  m_text: 'A clever woodland bird that watches from above and reacts quickly to movement.

    

    Crows
    travel in small groups and are often seen taking short flights between perches
    and open ground.

    Look near tree lines and open clearings. They are easiest
    to spot when they pause to observe the player.'
